aikit — AI Coding Agent CLI Installer & Manager  v1.15.0
Install, update, authenticate, and manage 31 AI coding agent CLIs from one tool.

Architecture:
    Agent registry → platform-aware install → auth multiplexing → web dashboard

Usage:
    aikit setup                     First-run interactive wizard
    aikit install [agents...]       Install agents (interactive multi-select if none)
    aikit update [agents...]        Update installed agents (all if none)
    aikit uninstall [agent...]      Remove agents
    aikit list                      Show all agents and installation status
    aikit auth [agent]              Configure authentication for an agent
    aikit serve                     Start web dashboard (http://localhost:8765)
    aikit doctor                    Diagnose environment and agents
    aikit config get/set/list       Manage configuration
    aikit gateway on/off/purge      Toggle the LiteLLM gateway (purge forgets creds)
    aikit gateway coverage          Show which agents route through the gateway (and which can't)

Dependencies:
    pip install rich requests flask readchar
"""

